post_title: Now Only 2 Players of Little Note With Higher Grades FS
post_content:
Fine examples of lesser known players slabbed by the good folks at SGC.

Looking for PPFF.  If you want G&S, you pay the fees (3%).  Willing to discuss other methods of payment.

Only 2 left.  They must be underpriced.:eek:

Shipping included.
